---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms of Use" description="EasyCalc terms of use. Read the conditions before using our free online calculators.">
  <div class="static-page">
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>
    <h2>1. Acceptance</h2>
    <p>By accessing and using EasyCalc (<strong>calculafacilito.netlify.app</strong>), you agree to these terms. If you disagree, please stop using the site.</p>
    <h2>2. Service description</h2>
    <p>EasyCalc provides free online calculation tools (percentages, loans, dates, converters, etc.) for informational and reference purposes.</p>
    <h2>3. Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p>Our calculator results are <strong>indicative only</strong>. EasyCalc does not guarantee absolute accuracy in all cases and is not responsible for financial, legal, or other decisions made based on our tool results.</p>
    <p>For important financial decisions (loans, investments, taxes), always consult a qualified professional.</p>
    <h2>4. Intellectual property</h2>
    <p>All content, design, and code on EasyCalc are the property of their creators. Reproduction without express authorization is prohibited.</p>
    <h2>5. Acceptable use</h2>
    <p>The site is for personal, non-commercial use. Attempting to damage, overload, or compromise the security of the site is prohibited.</p>
    <h2>6. Modifications</h2>
    <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes take effect upon publication on this page.</p>
    <h2>7. Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Use our <a href="/en/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
<style>
  .static-page { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 0; }
  .static-page h1 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
  .updated { font-size: .875rem; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .static-page h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 2rem 0 .75rem; color: #1e3a8a; }
  .static-page p { color: #374151; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
</style>
